parameters.query:
SELECT 
  COALESCE(ip_address, '{{ $json.client_ip }}') as ip_address,
  COALESCE(request_count, 0) as request_count,
  COALESCE(window_start, NOW()) as window_start,
  CASE 
    WHEN window_start IS NULL THEN 1
    WHEN window_start < NOW() - INTERVAL '{{ $('‚öôÔ∏è CONFIG').first().json.rate_limit_window_sec }} seconds' THEN 1
    WHEN request_count >= {{ $('‚öôÔ∏è CONFIG').first().json.rate_limit_max_requests }} THEN -1
    ELSE request_count + 1
  END as new_count
FROM (
  SELECT * 
  FROM {{ $('‚öôÔ∏è CONFIG').first().json.table_rate_limits }}
  WHERE ip_address = '{{ $json.client_ip }}'
    AND endpoint = 'verify-license'
  ORDER BY window_start DESC
  LIMIT 1
) sub
RIGHT JOIN (SELECT 1) dummy ON TRUE
LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO {{ $('‚öôÔ∏è CONFIG').first().json.table_rate_limits }} (ip_address, endpoint, request_count, window_start, created_at)
VALUES (
  '{{ $json.client_ip }}',
  'verify-license',
  1,
  NOW(),
  NOW()
)
ON CONFLICT (ip_address, endpoint) 
DO UPDATE SET
  request_count = CASE 
    WHEN {{ $('‚öôÔ∏è CONFIG').first().json.table_rate_limits }}.window_start < NOW() - INTERVAL '{{ $('‚öôÔ∏è CONFIG').first().json.rate_limit_window_sec }} seconds' THEN 1
    ELSE {{ $('‚öôÔ∏è CONFIG').first().json.table_rate_limits }}.request_count + 1
  END,
  window_start = CASE 
    WHEN {{ $('‚öôÔ∏è CONFIG').first().json.table_rate_limits }}.window_start < NOW() - INTERVAL '{{ $('‚öôÔ∏è CONFIG').first().json.rate_limit_window_sec }} seconds' THEN NOW()
    ELSE {{ $('‚öôÔ∏è CONFIG').first().json.table_rate_limits }}.window_start
  END
RETURNING ip_address, request_count, window_start;

SELECT 
  client_id,
  name,
  email,
  license_key,
  status,
  allowed_domains,
  features,
  expires_at,
  CASE 
    WHEN status != 'active' THEN 'inactive'
    WHEN expires_at IS NOT NULL AND expires_at < NOW() THEN 'expired'
    ELSE 'valid'
  END as license_status
FROM {{ $('‚öôÔ∏è CONFIG').first().json.table_clients }}
WHERE license_key = '{{ $json.license_key }}';
